DATASET LICENSES

OhioT1DM Dataset:
  This project uses the OhioT1DM dataset, which requires a separate access
  request or data-use process. The dataset is NOT included in this repository.
  Current access details are documented in docs/technical/dataset_guide.md.

PhysioCGM Dataset:
  Open-access dataset described in:
  "A multimodal physiological dataset for non-invasive blood glucose
  estimation", Scientific Data (2025), DOI: 10.1038/s41597-025-06090-6.
  The repository does not redistribute the raw files.

MIT-BIH Arrhythmia Database:
  Hosted via PhysioNet:
  https://physionet.org/content/mitdb/1.0.0/
  License: Open Data Commons Attribution License v1.0.

CHB-MIT Scalp EEG Database:
  Hosted via PhysioNet:
  https://physionet.org/content/chbmit/1.0.0/
  Access and citation details are documented in docs/technical/dataset_guide.md.

